title: Veggie Time
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Chinese, Thai, Fast food, Take-out, Malaysian, Asian Fusion, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg-options available. Food court shop with a few tables, reported added meat Feb 2015 and no longer pure veg. Features a buffet and a made-to-order menu for stir fry, noodle, and rice dishes. Dishes are labelled. Lots of vegetable and tofu dishes, no mock meat.
